472
00:39:30,359 --> 00:39:32,319
Xuan Ji.

473
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,109
I like you.

474
00:39:34,110 --> 00:39:38,201
More than anyone and anything.

475
00:39:40,879 --> 00:39:43,002
