476
00:39:43,759 --> 00:39:45,082
I hope that

477
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:47,939
you’ll always be mine alone.

478
00:39:56,600 --> 00:40:01,319
This hairpin is a love token
from my father to my mother.

479
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:03,399
I’ll give it to you now.

480
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:06,046
Si Feng.

481
00:40:06,047 --> 00:40:07,919
